{"tid":1068422,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《香港年度期待電影》","createTime":"2019-03-19T08:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T10:11:30.000Z","uid":226695,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c077a379d44b5ae66577dc74b70c58913ffa6d1a","tid":1068422,"uid":226695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:32:40.000Z","msg":"明日戰記<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUVG9Yj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUVG9Yj.jpg&h=0ba16a12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n投資：逾4.5億<br />\n導演：吳炫輝<br />\n演員：古天樂、劉青雲、劉嘉玲、謝君豪、姜皓文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lMFJijxmUFo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlMFJijxmUFo&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=8079e422\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lMFJijxmUFo</a><br />\n古天樂表示，希望透過這部電影，證明香港的特效已達國際水準<br />\n<br />\n風林火山<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C1xBYRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC1xBYRY.jpg&h=4d2729e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n投資：逾2億 <br />\n導演：麥浚龍<br />\n演員：金城武、梁家輝、劉青雲、古天樂、高圓圓、杜德偉、姜珮瑤、衛詩雅、黃偉文、韋羅莎、吳嘉龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q7mPsiP187g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dq7mPsiP187g&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=9e3bb13d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q7mPsiP187g</a><br />\n落雪的銅鑼灣景<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Xf75yg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Xf75yg.jpg&h=9be95de1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影片格調選用了導演麥浚龍最喜愛的冷酷黑白色調，雖然極為昏暗，但正好將警匪兩派對決時，劍拔弩張的氣氛完全展現出來，以帶出眾演員面臨生存的困局。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十分期待！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港電影回歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdf11a442a0058d567cd99d1793be3def892660","tid":1068422,"uid":226695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:35:12.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644c2420c09eace687075e32ffe14c50276c669d","tid":1068422,"uid":226695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:36:10.000Z","msg":"集氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c526efec702bd8de22f66c7d6c3c45d838f5d66","tid":1068422,"uid":226695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:42:27.000Z","msg":"支持支持！"},{"pid":"c683675083f70dba3f5058550358e966a64c1a11","tid":1068422,"uid":181905,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:43:20.000Z","msg":"明日戰記個故事設定係2055年 點解仲有現今D校車小巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008b6774a35ef452d191df333a2e5eef357a5b8d","tid":1068422,"uid":226695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c683675083f70dba3f5058550358e966a64c1a11","tid":1068422,"uid":181905,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:43:20.000Z","msg":"明日戰記個故事設定係2055年 點解仲有現今D校車小巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:44:54.000Z","msg":"你又岩WOR，但角色設計幾正，希望故事唔好老套！"},{"pid":"4246dba67b0bcd915b975225114e8b5fcdc3503f","tid":1068422,"uid":226695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/snEgYYx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsnEgYYx.jpg&h=02cf6779&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n型到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffcfe1ba30eeffcbe110b0320ac28107531857c","tid":1068422,"uid":226695,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T08:55